@startuml
title Check Availability - Sequence Design
autonumber
skinparam shadowing false

actor "Pet Owner / Receptionist" as User
participant "Web SPA" as Web
participant "api-gateway" as Gateway
participant "visits-service\nVisitController" as Visits
participant "RemoteClientsFacade" as Remote
participant "vets-service" as Vets
database "visits schema" as VisitDB

User -> Web: Select vet and date
Web -> Gateway: GET /api/v1/visits/availability
Gateway -> Visits: route
Visits -> Remote: getVetAvailability(vetId, date)
Remote -> Vets: GET /api/v1/vets/{id}/availability
Vets --> Remote: working slots
Visits -> VisitDB: load existing SCHEDULED/IN_PROGRESS visits
Visits -> Visits: subtract occupied 30-minute slots
Visits --> Web: available slots
@enduml
